* ============================================================================
* DotTalk++ Beta-0 Readiness Test
* File: beta0_readiness_test.dts
* Purpose:
*   Minimal integrated proof that DotTalk++ is a coherent Beta-0 system.
*
* Proves:
*   1) workspace bring-up
*   2) schema/metadata inspection
*   3) navigation
*   4) indexed order
*   5) key search
*   6) predicate filtering
*   7) relation wiring
*   8) relation traversal
*   9) tuple projection
*  10) table buffering + commit
*  11) help system integrity
*
* Notes:
*   - This is intended as a practical readiness script, not an exhaustive regression.
*   - It assumes the MCC-style dataset is present under the configured DBF root.
*   - It performs one reversible GPA edit and commits it.
* ============================================================================

SET ECHO ON

ECHO ===== BETA-0 READINESS TEST START =====

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 1 -- bring up dataset
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 1: SCHEMAS =====
SCHEMAS CLOSE
SCHEMAS OPEN DBF

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 2 -- select a table
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 2: SELECT / STATUS =====
SELECT STUDENTS
STATUS

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 3 -- inspect schema
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 3: STRUCT / FIELDS =====
STRUCT
FIELDS

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 4 -- navigation baseline
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 4: NAVIGATION =====
TOP
LIST 3
BOTTOM
LIST 1
TOP

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 5 -- activate indexed order
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 5: INDEXED ORDER =====
SET INDEX TO students.cdx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
TOP
LIST 5

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 6 -- key search
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 6: SEEK / DISPLAY =====
SEEK TAYLOR
DISPLAY

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 7 -- predicate filtering
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 7: SMARTLIST / PREDICATE =====
SMARTLIST 5 FOR GPA >= 3.5

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 8 -- build relation graph
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 8: SET RELATION / REL LIST =====
SET RELATION OFF ALL
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL
REL LIST

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 9 -- extend relation chain
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 9: RELATION CHAIN =====
REL ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
REL ADD CLASSES TASSIGN ON CLS_ID
REL ADD TASSIGN TEACHERS ON TID
REL LIST ALL

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 10 -- relation traversal
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 10: REL ENUM =====
LOCATE LNAME = TAYLOR
REL ENUM LIMIT 5 ENROLL CLASSES TASSIGN TEACHERS TUPLE STUDENTS.SID,STUDENTS.LNAME,TEACHERS.LNAME

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 11 -- buffering demonstration
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 11: TABLE BUFFER / COMMIT =====
LOCATE LNAME = TAYLOR
TABLE ON
REPLACE GPA WITH GPA + 0.01
TABLE STALE
COMMIT
REPLACE GPA WITH GPA - 0.01
COMMIT
TABLE OFF

* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Step 12 -- help system integrity
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ===== STEP 12: HELP SYSTEM =====
HELP REL
HELP TUPLE
HELP /FOX SEEK
HELP GIANT

ECHO ===== BETA-0 READINESS TEST END =====
